𝗠𝗮𝘅𝗶𝗺𝘂𝗺 𝗻𝘂𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝗼𝗳 𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘀𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝘀𝘂𝗺𝗺𝗲𝗿 𝗱𝗮𝘆𝘀 

sis-agroclimatic-indicators

origin: hadgem2_es_model
HadGEM2- Hadley Centre Global Environment Model version 2

Temporal Resolution - Seasonal
2011 -  04 (April), 07 (July),  10 (October)
2012 -  01(January), 04 (April), 07 (July),  10 (October)
2013 .............. 2040

computed for 3 month periods representing the standard meteorological seasons:
Dec, Jan, Feb (DJF)
Mar, Apr, May (MAM)
Jun, Jul, Aug (JJA)
Sep, Oct, Nov (SON)

𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗮 𝗔𝘃𝗮𝗶𝗹𝗮𝗯𝗶𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆:
2011-2040 (29 Years)
3 bands for 2011
4 bands for 1 year (i.e) - 29x4 - 116 bands (+3 bands -2011)
Total 119 bands

𝗠𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗼𝗱𝘀 𝘁𝗼 𝗲𝘅𝘁𝗿𝗮𝗰𝘁 𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗱𝘀:
1. Using FOR loop through bands to extract the bands (time consuming)
2. Parallel Processing (Parallely clips the bands)
